{"tid":314371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩疑在洲際導彈旁食煙　燃料高度易燃","createTime":"2017-07-09T06:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T06:17:48.000Z","uid":20933,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0630e61c42e042fe033be5cc6ae20658f564d306","tid":314371,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170709/large/1499570706_d702.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170709%2Flarge%2F1499570706_d702.jpg&h=0f2925fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北韓上周二宣稱首度成功試射洲際彈道導彈（ICBM），官方發佈的片段顯示，領導人金正恩親自監督導彈發射。有報道指，由金正恩的動作看來，懷疑他竟然在導彈旁邊抽煙，卻沒有人上前阻止。<br />\n<br />\n朝中社發放的片段可見金正恩與彈道導彈「火星-14型」（Hwasong-14）的基座相距僅數米，他的右手似乎手持香煙，在導彈周圍行來行去，抽了一口煙後手部自然垂下。但片段中他背對鏡頭，未見到噴煙的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n報道指「火星-14型」的液體燃料火箭引擎尚未經過測試，液體燃料高度易燃同時具有揮發性，應該遠離任何火種，但當時似乎沒有人勸金正恩不要抽煙。<br />\n<br />\n北韓發射洲際彈道導彈後宣佈試射成功，更自稱為核強國，能打擊世界任何地區，引起國際社會強烈抨擊，美國及南韓周三聯合進行火砲和導彈軍演回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170709&amp;guid=56932641&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170709%26guid%3D56932641%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=3%2Ffu82qcZ4jJTgeXT1c27HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f54d4b08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170709%26guid%3D56932641%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=91f3bf6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170709&amp;guid=56932641&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"6abd18fe9782eddcc5c07bfb6d1d4369bb48c7e4","tid":314371,"uid":20227,"like":177,"dislike":1,"score":176,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:51:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1ae24d8e368c10713d1e14b742599c66ca29f96","tid":314371,"uid":57962,"